Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(751.875,510)}Tales of a Gutsy Ninja -\N{\i1}Jiraiya Ninja Scrolls - Part 1\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that there are\Nonly two bells means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One person will lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very sharp, Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say! If I get a bell,\Nyou'll go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose,\Ndon't bother me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So many openings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won the bet, Jiraiya!\NYou get to go to the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, flat-chested plywood Tsunade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!\NYou egg-headed perv!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunade and Orochimaru may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a ninja keep falling\Ninto such obvious traps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps what you lack\Nis a purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We'll try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so excited. Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Summoning Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a blood contract with an animal,\N and summon them at will using the Transportation Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a contract\Nwith that one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way that every man is destined to a different fate,\N so too is the animal to whom he is intertwined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then which is my animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you can make a contract,\N you need to be more adept at molding chakra and sealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Not more training!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You will always find the answer\Nin your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya had found a purpose and from that day on,\N he began taking his training seriously. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mold more chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Study up on sealing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I must master\Nthe Transportation Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I be able to\Nmake a contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I put up with\N{\i1}this rough training?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I were to have a boyfriend,\N {\i1}I'd choose Orochimaru over {\i1}an egghead perv like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to become the ultimate ninja\N and sweep Tsunade off her feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that that's settled,\Nthere's no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's discovered his purpose\Nfor becoming a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And not just Tsunade,\N {\i1}I'm gonna get all the pretty girls {\i1}to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see...\N{\i1}Concentrate my chakra and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the seal is boar, dog,\N{\i1}bird, monkey, sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's no telling what will happen if you use the\N Transportation Technique without making a contract first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the great Master Jiraiya,\Nshall take over this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! I guess that'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! A-A talking toad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?\N To think, a human would really come to Mount Myoboku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Fukasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...so you've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk as though\Nyou've been expecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I knew you were coming.\NThe Great Lord Elder predicted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human child will stumble\N{\i1}into Mount Myoboku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I will give that child the power\N{\i1}of the toad and a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is the dream which\N{\i1}I dreamt of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My very own prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If that human is me...\Nthen what is {\i1}my{\i0} prophecy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stay here and train,\N and wait for the Great Lord Elder's prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind to become strong\N so that I'll be popular with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in getting popular\Nwith frogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit complaining!\NThis is your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My destiny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You managed to come\Nto Mount Myoboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is proof that you were indeed\Nthe chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The chosen one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Training here and becoming strong...\N{\i1}That's pretty tempting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day forward,\NJiraiya divided his time between
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Myoboku, the land of toads,\Nand the Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent the days of his youth\Nin both Sage and ninjutsu training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not to be as simple as\NJiraiya had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've definitely gotten stronger\N{\i1}since coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsunade is as cold as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I was destined to be {\i1}the chosen one,\N {\i1}should my purpose simply {\i1}be to impress a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that the only reason why\N{\i1}I'm trying to become strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya! Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya, the Great Lord Elder\Nhas summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Lord Elder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.\NHe has seen your prophecy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For real, Bunta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good. I'm glad you've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Lord Elder, it's Jiraiya!\NThis is Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Right!\NMy, how you've grown...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah, you're the one who summoned him,\Nya great senile old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Senile old geezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma, how dare ya call\Nthe Great Lord Elder a senile old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, let's not fight.\NSpouses oughta get along...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Lord Elder had\Na dream about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are aware,\Nit is a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now tell you.\NIn my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you, who are solely pervy, will still\Nmanage to become a splendid ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And in time, you will have\Nyour own disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Solely pervy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't believe he remembers\N{\i1}that particular detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That disciple will become a ninja who will\N bring about a great change to the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A great change?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Either great stability\Nor great destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The likes of which this world\Nhas never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those two?\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You will guide that revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The day will come when you will\Nbe forced to make a critical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your choice shall decide\Nwhich way the change goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What must I do...?\NIn order to make the right choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dream, you traveled the world,\Nwriting books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Books? Whatever for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it will be a journey around\N the world to see all things in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Lord Elder, have your prophecies\Never not come to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya, you are leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point in my life, there's no way I can\N guide someone who will be a revolutionary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let alone make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I need more time to see many more things,\N and meet different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in the Great Lord Elder's dream, I shall journey\N throughout the world and perhaps, write a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that is my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,While Jiraiya journeyed and searched for the\N meaning behind the Great Lord Elder's dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the state of the world grew\Nsteadily more chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The peace that had prevailed among\Nthe Five Great Nations became fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aggression between lands\Nincreased as did internal strife,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people began to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man...\NWhy are you traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone saw me in a dream.\N And just like in that dream, I journey from land to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what's the matter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have one. It's milk candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A puppet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this child tells me...\NDestiny is not something you search for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny is something you latch onto\Nwhen it presents itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The age of war is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechanical skills are useless in times of peace,\N but some feudal lord may pay a high price for my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he is a ninja too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has chosen to ride the wave\N{\i1}to the age of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that will only...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just an ordinary village!\NWhy would a ninja...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This shuriken jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are from the Fuma, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why attack people who\Nare living in peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are also a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am journeying in search of the one\Nwho will become my disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Why waste time\Non such a tedious thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The balance of power between lands has become\N shaky and we are on the verge of a great war...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That village was also destroyed due\Nto a tip that ninja had infiltrated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because of a tip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's destroy, or be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in a world where\Nyou'll die if you hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Smoke Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a ninja too,\NI cannot let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up...\NThis is our fate as ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...on me giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you bring me down,\N another assassin will attack the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we are cursed to live in this ninja world,\N there will be no peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Great Toad Sage's\N{\i1}prophecy said that I am destined
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to train the revolutionary\N{\i1}who will bring peace to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, I haven't even encountered\N{\i1}this disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Already at this time,\Nbattles were inevitably being fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya was also forced to take\Na short break from his journey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and returned to the Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at war...after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to erase this sadness\N{\i1}from the ninja world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must find the revolutionary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must choose the one\N{\i1}who will bring peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames of war finally drew\Nin Jiraiya and his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This would come to be known\Nas the Third Great Ninja War.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly afterwards, the three would come\N to be known as the "Legendary Sannin."
Comment: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:08.56,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(752.813,520)}Tales of a Gutsy Ninja -\N{\i1}Jiraiya Ninja Scrolls -Part 2\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I predict the Hidden Leaf shall\Nemerge victorious from this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I shall let you three live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want your sympathy!\NWe can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You three are strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived even this battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hanzo, hereby name you\Nthe "Hidden Leaf's Sannin."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for your lives,\Ntell me your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it really end with\Nthe Hidden Leaf's victory like he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it does, then what?\NWill you set out on another journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Set out on my travels and\Nwrite another book...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you settle down\Nin the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though\NI haven't encountered it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, your destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even little mice can be from\Nthe Hidden Rain Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hide. Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were killed by ninja\Nbecause of this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...have some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato, Konan, come on out!\NThey don't seem like bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We already gave you food!\NWhy are you following us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. This is for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's origami...\Nfolded from the bread wrapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us ninjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all ninja from\Nthe Hidden Leaf, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I kill these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen many war orphans.\NIt's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They would be better off if we just put\N them out of their misery right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru, enough!\NYou go on ahead with Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here and look after them\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just until they can take better\Ncare of themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is also part of destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grilled fish in an instant with\Nmy Fire Style Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei! I've gotten the hang of fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying! You're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of guys like you that men of\N the Hidden Rain are considered cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are unstable among three of the Great\N Nations that surround the Hidden Rain Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But this war won't drag out much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time you are grown,\N there will be mutual understanding and peace will-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We all lost our families!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a mutual understanding,\N it's only after they go through what we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to get even, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But...I know that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why wars will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This land is always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna change this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Jiraiya Sensei...!\NPlease teach us ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have any ideas for my novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there is a mutual understanding,\N {\i1}it's only after they go through {\i1}what we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why wars will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll protect everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want the hero to wipe away\N{\i1}the hatred and bring about peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then...how can I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya Sensei, help!\NYahiko and Nagato are in trouble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way, Konan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.66,0:24:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This leftover ninja told us to hand\Nover our food...and valuables.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a chunin from the Hidden Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.38,0:24:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did Nagato...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.26,0:24:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-Those eyes...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:24:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He couldn't...possibly be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.35,0:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That shape... That ripple pattern...\N{\i1}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.39,0:25:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.69,0:25:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Said to hold the most noble of\N{\i1}the three great Visual Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.74,0:25:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Rinnegan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.95,0:25:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sage of the Six Paths,\N{\i1}said to be the father of all ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that the Sage possessing {\i1}the Rinnegan\N eye {\i1}developed all the jutsu known to us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.75,0:25:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rumored to always appear {\i1}when the world becomes\N corrupt, {\i1}capable of being both {\i1}a godlike force of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.25,0:25:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and an all-obliterating instrument\N{\i1}of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.78,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always believed it as a mere legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But here is someone who actually\N{\i1}possesses the Rinnegan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.59,0:25:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now tell you...\NIn my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.71,0:25:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who are solely pervy, will still manage\Nto become a splendid ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And in time, you will have\Nyour own disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.52,0:25:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That disciple will become a ninja who will\N bring about a great change to the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.85,0:26:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You will guide that revolutionary...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.07,0:26:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The day will come when you will be\Nforced to make a critical selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.59,0:26:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could Nagato be this revolutionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps I have found my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.32,0:26:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to teach you ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.68,0:26:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.38,0:26:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You may encounter another life-threatening\Nsituation like that last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.92,0:26:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is ninjutsu for self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.49,0:26:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.39,0:26:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving us last time, Nagato!\NSorry I called you a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.63,0:26:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time anything happens,\NI'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.05,0:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, Yahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.84,0:26:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? But Nagato is stronger\Nthan you, Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.30,0:27:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna train starting now\Nand I'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.41,0:27:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You always exaggerate, Konan!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.26,0:27:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.44,0:27:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The first lesson is on molding chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, Sensei!\N- Yes, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.73,0:27:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.76,0:27:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about that incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.79,0:27:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.39,0:27:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When that man hurt Yahiko,\NI was so mad at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.05,0:27:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything went blank in my head...\NI didn't know what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, the man was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.91,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I got so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.29,0:28:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This hatred made me lose myself...\Nand I killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.89,0:28:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did was wrong!\NThere had to be a better way--!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.22,0:28:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know\Nif it was right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.71,0:28:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to you, Yahiko didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.92,0:28:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You protected your friend.\N That had to be the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.98,0:28:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can blame you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.55,0:28:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are hurt, you learn to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.02,0:28:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, when\Nyou hurt someone, you are resented.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.75,0:28:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you start to feel guilty as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.75,0:28:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding such pain enables\Nyou to be kind to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.59,0:28:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.45,0:28:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.17,0:28:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.71,0:28:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing up? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.59,0:29:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you need to figure out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.09,0:29:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Konan and I were crying because \Nwe were so hungry and Yahiko saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.19,0:29:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole food from others to feed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.24,0:29:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to protect those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.49,0:29:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of pain\NI have to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.32,0:29:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.09,0:29:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"TALES OF A GUTSY NINJA" BY JIRAIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.18,0:29:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Style: Raging Waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.44,0:29:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Style: Gale Palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.69,0:29:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.03,0:30:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.85,0:30:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even able to take down\Nmy Shadow Clone now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.00,0:30:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can return to my village\Nwithout any worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.70,0:30:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.79,0:30:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are on your own from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.56,0:30:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well these past three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.29,0:30:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Yahiko.\NOr people will call you a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.19,0:30:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Konan... You're gonna grow up\Nto be a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.65,0:30:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.52,0:30:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a poor land.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.73,0:30:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's more sadness\Nand tough times up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.95,0:30:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, you have the strength\Nto change this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.19,0:30:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato... You three have grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:30:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.38,0:31:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.47,0:31:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after Jiraiya returned to the village,\Nthe Third Great Ninja War raged on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.94,0:31:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunade! Orochimaru! Ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.49,0:31:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Summoning Jutsu!\N- Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.35,0:31:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf's Sannin distinguished\Nthemselves in many battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.67,0:31:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving legends in their wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.15,0:31:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All this fighting...\NHow long must it continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.05,0:31:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What must be done to stop the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... As if there's a way to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.22,0:32:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate only gives birth\Nto even more hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.61,0:32:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.61,0:32:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to stop it.\NBut peace will certainly come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.74,0:32:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there are those who\Nbelieve that, there is hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.17,0:32:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.92,0:32:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.79,0:32:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried my best to make\Nthe right choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.52,0:32:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that was what destiny\Nhad in store for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.42,0:33:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally...\NI thought I did what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.58,0:33:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps,\NI was wrong yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.62,0:33:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it\Nas long as you keep believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.69,0:33:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I guess I'm still in\Nthe middle of my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Great Ninja War dragged on and the\N one who guided Hidden Leaf Village to victory
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.97,0:33:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was another one of Jiraiya's disciples...\NMinato Namikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.32,0:33:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was long. Too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.00,0:33:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.78,0:33:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...\NMaybe set out on another journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.55,0:33:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll find a disciple who\Ncan change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.35,0:33:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your destiny?\NThe destiny of Jiraiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.39,0:34:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.02,0:34:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... What a strange man you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.34,0:34:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You walk the path of the ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.35,0:34:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want someone\Nto take over after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.82,0:34:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To gather all the jutsu in this world\Nand master them...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.75,0:34:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my only goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.79,0:34:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you master them all,\Nhumans are not immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.50,0:34:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.19,0:34:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that...
